<br />November 29, 2002, The US Patent and Trademark Office has received an application from SoE for the name to be trademarked. <br />
<br />
Everquest: The Lost Dungeons of Norrath <br />
<br />
Under Goods and Services: IC 009. US 021 023 026 036 038. G &amp; S: COMPUTER GAME SOFTWARE AND VIDEO GAME SOFTWARE; OPERATING A REAL TIME GAME FOR OTHERS OVER GLOBAL AND LOCAL AREA COMPUTER NETWORKS <br />
<br />
At this time it is unknown WHAT this name is for but the Classification of it is Exactly the same classification that Planes of Power and Ruins of Kunark received, so Stay tuned for Further Information... <br />
<br />
